OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK steel giant set to cut  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fup to 2,000 jobs           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, British Steel has confirmed it plans to
OL,6, close down its blast furnaces in       
OL,7, Scunthorpe, putting up to 2,000 jobs at
OL,8, risk.                                  
OL,10,FThey will be replaced with two electric
OL,11,Farc furnaces - one at Scunthorpe and   
OL,12,Fone at Teesside.                       
OL,14,FThe company said its #1.25bn proposal  
OL,15,Fwould make British Steel "a clean,     
OL,16,Fgreen and sustainable business".       
OL,18,FBut it said the plans were still       
OL,19,F"subject to appropriate support" from  
OL,20,Fthe UK government.                     
